- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper deals with managing the radio resources in a distributed manner. 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is also a possible category as the paper proposes a multi-agent framework for radio resource management. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with optimizing the performance of wireless networks.
